column5: Almost literally ran into our Rick this morning at the local SDM. He looked at me and I stared him down but didnt waiver!  Didnt get to exchange pleasantries as he seemed to be in a hurry but he looked in good health!  Keep doing what youre doing Rick as it seems to be beneficial. Too bad we didnt get to talk, maybe next time...
excuse my ignorance but what's an SDM?
It does sound nasty... eh Roger!
hahaha why do I even ask
I'd presume... Shoppers Drug Mart Roger..
It's odd that that would be the first thing to pop up in your mind.
It's obvious that you've never met Leah!!!
How do you know it was the first thing !!!
You guys are definitely off the WALL!  Shoppers Drug Mart!
Don't tell me you just now noticed that?
